phrases: A person must first experience pain to be able to pilot Nyapollon.
I will defeat all of the Nyangoro aliens.
I do not know how to respond to that kind of confession...
You are being a wimp, kouhai-kun!
Take your rejection like a man, for the sake of Earth's future!
I get that a lot, but I am afraid not.
I thought you might still be buzzing from the Nyapollon experience.
Please participate in the following survey about Milky Way Cat Nyapollon.
This is the majority of them.
Looks like everyone enjoyed the show.
It was because everyone else did such a great job...
It did not matter who was in my position.
The end result would have been the same.
That is very modest of you.
I do feel a little more confident now.
Are you going to reapply to the Let us Make a Game!
I submitted my application right after that.
I am waiting for the results.
Akasaka told me to look over the notes from the Nyapollon review meeting...
so that I would not make the same mistakes again...
and I wrote a pitch based on that.
So, how confident are you feeling?
That was pretty bold of Rita-san.
She is been texting me constantly since that moment,
so I finally gave her Akasaka's number.
It would be nice if those two could get it together properly.
What are you two doing together?
Mashiro asked me if I knew where Kanda-kun was...
I figured you might be up here, so I brought her.
You came looking for me because you needed something, right?
What am I going to do, kouhai-kun?
My once-in-a-lifetime opportunity has presented itself!
I do not understand what you are talking
Why are you pouncing me this early in the day?
I could not wait until tonight.
I feel like I am in danger, so I will be staying out tonight.
Here, Jin, I made you lunch.
Was not Jin-san just eating bread?
Did it win your stomach over?
I have not eaten any yet.
Did you see something you want to eat?
What did Shiina come up here to do?
I will make it even more gorgeous next time!
You do not understand Mashiro, do you?
Look forward to tomorrow's lunch, Jin!
I do, but I am not telling.
It is not like you to say something like that.
Aoyama, you are kind of mean to me sometimes, are not you?
I do not know what you are talking about!
Are you saying you have plans, Yayoi?
I am throwing a party for the Softball Club.
What will you do about him?
Do not you know that people suspect...
You have got to get your act together!
It is not fair to Miyahara, either.
How do you know about that?!
It is obvious just by looking at Miyahara-kun.
In any case, you have got to make your intentions clear!
I am not surprised Kamiigusa-senpai sent you that.
I have got something I have been meaning to give you.
If you would like, why do not you go see this with someone?
Asami-san invited me, but she cannot make it now.
It would be wrong of me to invite someone else, so you can have them.
The performance is on Christmas Eve.
You have got to use the tools at your disposal.
what were you going to do if I had taken off...
my underwear while I was changing?
It would be too late by then!
Are you going to say you do not need anything again?
Promise you will not get angry.
If you are telling me that,
you must be about to say something crazy.
Then, do not lead off with a weird statement like that!
I want to make a lunch.
I want to make a lunch.
You idiot, do not grab my arm!
Great potential lies within all humans.
However, there are some things people cannot do.
These are things you have to accept!
Jin-san, why are you putting an apron on her?!
I never dreamed you would be so forward.
That is not what I meant!
Shiina and cooking seriously do not mix!
It looks to me like you are ready to make me cook!
I have got to go meet Rumi-san.
Why are you talking like that?
Do not you need to work on your manuscript?
You must be behind schedule because of the culture festival...
I will work on my manuscript later.
You want me to teach you, right?
Your main dish will be fried mackerel.
We will also make fried eggs and a salad.
Let us start with the eggs.
I will start with the eggs.
You do not have to repeat what I say.
Crack the egg by hitting it against a bowl like this,
and then, break it in half with both hands.
who is just sent their kid out on an errand for the first time.
Only after you have leveled up your cooking skills.
That is all you can do.
Just how much do you like them?
So much that I cannot sleep at night.
That is how you hold it when attacking someone!
Do not point it at me!
What exactly are you planning to cook?!
Do you want to be cooked?
Fold the fingers of your free hand when you use a knife.
Whatever you do, do not cut yourself.
Did I win your stomach over?
If that is all it takes to win my stomach,
I would be the guy who was won over by a cucumber farmer.
What could you possibly have understood...
just by cutting off the end of a cucumber?!
I will cut some more, then.
You klutz, let me see that!
Will you be able to finish your manuscript?
I have the cover left to do.
Sorata, do not you want me to cook?
You do not need to injure yourself any more than you did today.
What do you mean by that?
Up until recently, it seemed like she lived solely to draw manga...
I want you for my Christmas present, Onii-chan.
Who do you want to speak to?
I just had a supernatural experience!
I called the number in my contacts list,
but it connected me to someone
And that is what you call a supernatural experience.
Um, do you have a minute?
Will her manuscript be all right?
From the looks of it, she will finish up today.
The cut on her finger does not seem to be causing any problems.
I want you to give me your honest opinion.
How do you feel about Shiina-san now?
I mean, has she gotten prettier or cuter,
or do you get the urge to hold her?
Wh-What are you trying to get me to say?
Do not you think Shiina-san has changed a little lately?
When I first met her, she had the face of an artist.
A strange feeling washed over me while talking to her.
She was looking at me with those lucid eyes,
I got the same feeling the first time I met her.
I want to make a lunch.
I will work on my manuscript later.
When I look at Shiina now, something feels off.
No, that is not it, either.
It just... well, it irritates me.
Before, it seemed like the only thing she thought about...
was manga, and nothing else mattered.
But then she suddenly says she wants to cook...
the current Shiina is not the real Shiina...
I actually think her current behavior is normal.
Normal for a girl, I mean.
It is important for a girl who is spent her whole life studying art...
to have normal high school experiences...
and learn what it means to be normal.
But if that causes her to lose her unique outlook on the world...
I have been thinking about things an editor should not worry about.
Her talents and experiences will not falter on her now.
I kind of understand what you are saying...
Kanda-kun, which is the Shiina-san you like?
But in this case, if you choose either answer, it means you like her...
I feel more at ease around...
the old Shiina than the new one.
Yeah, but what are you doing?
What if you hurt yourself again and it does not heal...
within a day or two next time?
You focused on raising the quality as much as you could!
People who have been allowed to draw should not slack off!
In that case, get out from inside of me!
I do not know what this feeling is...
I know it is a little early, but...
the publisher's having an end-of-year party.
I forgot to give it to Shiina-san, so could you give it to her?
Kouhai-kun, I need your advice about something!
Why are you Santa in a miniskirt?
Only a few more nights until Christmas!
It is still more than a month away.
He might already have plans for Christmas Eve.
I mean, it is hard to invite him when we are not even dating...
Misaki-senpai wanted my advice about something.
How can I make my feelings reach Jin?
You are not dressed like someone who is worried.
I am sending out such passionate signals,
but Jin's too dense to notice!
So, these passionate feelings you are trying to send him...
You know I wrote I love you on his lunch, right?
I even put a marriage registration form in his shoe locker.
around the back of the school and confessed my feelings,
all he said was: It is cold.
And when I confessed my feelings behind the gym,
all he said was: I am tired.
I have done everything I can, but he thinks it is all a joke!
That is why I have decided to resort to my final option.
On Christmas Eve, I want you to leave me alone with Jin.
She had her answer before she even asked for my advice.
Can we go... to your room?
Why do not you come in?
I have two tickets to a play.
I was wondering if you would go with me.
It is actually on Christmas Eve...
Are you sure you want to make plans with me?
I am sure everyone else has plans, so why not?
If you really do not trust me, we can pinky swear it.
Why am I anxious on Christmas Eve?
This will be my first time spending Christmas with a girl!
This is a big step up!
I guess I should recite some sutras to calm down...
